<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy - BlogMaster</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .privacy-policy {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .privacy-policy h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      background-color:#003cff;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration-color: #f8f9fa;
    
    }
    .privacy-policy h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .privacy-policy p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #333;
    }
    .privacy-policy ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .privacy-policy ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .contact-section {
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-section a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include("nav")-%>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Section -->
  <section class="privacy-policy">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how BlogMaster collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our website.</p>

      <!-- Information Collection -->
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, and contact details when you register or contact us.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website, such as pages visited and time spent on the site.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies to enhance your experience and analyze website traffic.</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- How We Use Information -->
      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve our services.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you, including responding to your inquiries.</li>
        <li>To analyze website usage and improve user experience.</li>
        <li>To send promotional emails (only if you opt-in).</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Data Security -->
      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take the security of your data seriously. We implement industry-standard measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

      <!-- Third-Party Services -->
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party services (e.g., Google Analytics) to analyze website traffic. These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.</p>

      <!-- Your Rights -->
      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access and update your personal information.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data.</li>
        <li>Opt-out of receiving promotional emails.</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@blogmaster.com">info@blogmaster.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  

  <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <%- include("footer")-%>
</body>
</html>